original_title: Tattness: The Other Side of Hell: The Documentary
overview: The Documentary outlines the rise to success of Keith "Tattness" McCleary. From growing up in an abusive home to living on the streets to achieving success and becoming friends with so many well known celebrities. A tale of true hardship that will make you be inspired, cry and laugh. This is a story you do not want to miss.
title: Tattness: The Other Side of Hell: The Documentary
